what could u buy in a store or pet shop to keep nails trimmed so u dont have to cut them for parakeets we are looking for something that way we dont have to trim other then get something from the store or pet place so we dont have to take them to the vet yes they make sandpaper perches they also make concrete perches which are supposed to do the same thing you should be able to use an emery board or diamond file to file do a keet's nails just be sure not to trim them too short even a few drops of blood lost from a too short nail clipping can be serious and require a trip to the vet if you would like to see some articles on trimming a bird's nails just e mail me i can point you to a great yahoo group that has several such articles in its files and lots of friendly knowledgeable bird owners who can help you with questions good luck Manicure Ferret Neopets Parrot Swift Vets and POWs for Truth RuneScape quests Pet skunk Horseshoe RuneScape economy Garfield Knife Woodworking Animal Crossing Trent Reznor Baroque chess Nail (anatomy) Nine Inch Nails Philadelphia Phillies Microchip implant (animal) Password Cat Eaton's MapleStory Guinea pig Wal-Mart Upholstery Pet Pet store Pretty Good Privacy RuneScape skills Drill bit Dead Parrot Poker jargon 2000 Australian Grand Prix Pedicure RuneScape Classified information Online Copyright Infringement Liability Limitation Act Floppy disk Textile manufacturing Falconry Team Fortress Classic Killian documents Patent Shogi Family Guy Johnny the Homicidal Maniac Mail Domestic rabbit Shopping Alexandrine Parakeet The Apprentice 2 Tori shogi Bird Yu-Gi-Oh! anime, manga or movie only characters Hamster Taxicab Final Fantasy XI Trademark Beard RuneScape Mini-Games Taikyoku shogi Equine conformation File system Sears Holdings Corporation Best Buy Coffin Charles Goodyear Our Gang Wheel of Fortune Northern Mockingbird Nail disease Nail (engineering) Ballwin, Missouri United States Postal Service Wa shogi Little Britain Havanese Judkins shogi Co